## add custom logging level

```python
BIGINFO=25
logging.addLevelName(BIGINFO, 'BIGINFO')
def big_info(self, message, *args, **kws):
    if self.isEnabledFor(BIGINFO):
        self._log(BIGINFO, message, args, **kws)
logging.Logger.big_info = big_info
```